    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_XmcLJZvRWZDm8QxT",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>\"This is the only watch that&apos;s actually kept up with me. I&apos;ve dropped it, slammed it, scratched the hell out of it and it just keeps going. It&apos;s like it laughs in the face of abuse. Told all my guys to grab one too.\"</p>"
