    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_XGJxJlDGeDNJNkpp",
      "label": "Heading 1 → Vitals⁺ & Biotic⁺ bundle",
      "default": "<p>DROP TEST</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_ams5aoVJQbgZk3PG",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>No worries, this watch took a tumble and brushed it off. The shockproof design keeps the screen clear and sensors accurate.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "video_FAsHqklaTwWrmG9D",
      "label": "Video"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_zd8uXauI4qaYebLI",
      "label": "Heading 1 → Vitals⁺ & Biotic⁺ bundle",
      "default": "<p>DUMBBELL TEST</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_ULeuOdkj16OuI7x8",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Serious impact? No problem. The reinforced body and durable materials make the Carbinox Blaze practically indestructible.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "video_uk7npn6wJcelWbZd",
      "label": "Video"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_WD3I2V6XPgXV2nnT",
      "label": "Heading 1 → Vitals⁺ & Biotic⁺ bundle",
      "default": "<p>STRAP FLEXIBILITY TEST</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_ifeU9ggo83j3mimm",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>The Carbinox Blaze straps are ultra-flexible and tough — built to move with you without sacrificing comfort.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "video",
      "id": "video_Sov9VrOYsddDtpN1",
      "label": "Video"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_RNyrUWT99oYeroHv",
      "label": "Heading 1 → Vitals⁺ & Biotic⁺ bundle",
      "default": "<p>FRYING EGGS TEST </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_sXskEPXMTACKLC1G",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Heat and egg-resistant, the Blaze can handle wild challenges. Maybe don’t cook with it daily… but it’ll survive if you do!</p>"
    },
